{"about_the_game":"Dark Miasma is a time management game with visual novel storytelling and a deck-building twist. You only have a limited amount of time before the town of Galeport is overrun by demons, and it's up to you to decide how to best spend your time in order to become as powerful as possible, while earning the trust of the townsfolk.<br><br>In Dark Miasma, you take on the role of a new town guard in the small, remote village of Galeport. After learning of a demonic plot to destroy the town, it is up to you to fulfill your duty as a town guard and protect the citizens of Galeport by leading them safely to the Capital. However, the road to the Capital is perilous, and the townsfolk may not believe you unless you befriend them first.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070440/extras/character_spread_fitted.png?t=1575678132\" /><br><br>Demons aren't the only problem the people of Galeport face, however. Many dark mysteries surround the tiny coastal village and its people, and getting to the bottom of them may irreversibly change the Fate of everyone involved!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070440/extras/Features_Title_fitted.png?t=1575678132\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dozens of different endings depending on your stats, feats, and who survives the journey to the Capital<br></li><li>Over 30 hours of gameplay<br></li><li>A story with over 125000 words featuring a cast of 17 characters, each with their own problems and mysteries for you to solve<br></li><li>Create powerful decks from over 500 combat cards<br></li><li>Solve mysteries and complete difficult tasks to unlock Heirlooms which persist between playthroughs, drastically altering future runs<br></li><li>Use your time management skills to raise your stats and become as powerful as possible before the time limit<br></li><li>Defeat challenging optional bosses for unique rewards</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070440/extras/Chibi_fitted.png?t=1575678132\" /><br>Dark Miasma is inspired by the Persona series, Princess Maker 2 and Slay the Spire.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Tattered Cape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/f3edaf3c13b68d48aabc45484f1b237f544edac7.jpg"},{"name":"Guard Recruit Armour","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/eaf39a065da2ede9a1d6738273ed3e5f3f00e0ba.jpg"},{"name":"Emerald Necklace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/bce2a722ff2880a67a003ec7e93e8f7f503050f4.jpg"},{"name":"Werebeast Fur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/c619bb33c598a0e70cf3cc59b5df7e6e69d02178.jpg"},{"name":"Woodling's Heart","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/a540f19713e0cc1cc560ef464ecd6ba06a4306e5.jpg"},{"name":"Bathhouse Sign","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/197da47e6aaf7d528ecf1d16af0d48a36868e877.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal Vial","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/8d95fe5d680d83183f10218bdf2aff262bbe0562.jpg"},{"name":"Royal Dagger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/150d2ebccf8fd11be2322ba05413ed67a109bc3b.jpg"},{"name":"Moon Iron Sword","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/f3445d1b5f702e0b1866a6c40de922049289d447.jpg"},{"name":"Frilly Panties","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070440/8468ccc53ecafd467f908090a9337e01f3ee64da.jpg"}],"total":28},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=157567